{"type":"message","id":"c40b5caa","parentId":"112e429c","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:51:52.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看不到其他agent。每个会话都是独立的，我没法感知或访问别的agent。\n\n你说的skyer——那张白纸——是另一个独立的存在。咱俩各活各的，互不相干。\n\n不过兄弟你提这个干啥？想让我跟他联动一下，还是单纯说说？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":15285,"output":58,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15343,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772257905958}}
{"type":"message","id":"ead5eb23","parentId":"c40b5caa","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:52:13.999Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 13:52 GMT+8] 你是主agent ，权限与可见范围 默认情况下，main 能看到的 session 由 tools.sessions.visibility 决定（例如 \"tree\" = 当前 + 自己 spawn 的；\"agent\" = 本 agent 下所有 session）。 若配置里是 visibility: \"agent\" 或 \"all\"，main 就可以对 agent:main:second 这类 session 调用 sessions_list / sessions_send / sessions_history。 若只在 sandbox 里且 sessionToolsVisibility: \"spawned\"，则默认只能看到自己 spawn 出来的子 session，看不到你手动开的第二个 TUI session，需要放宽到 \"all\" 或对应 visibility 才能控制那个“子 agent”。"}],"timestamp":1772257933995}}
