{"type":"message","id":"482b36aa","parentId":"73c6be33","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:59:33.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"改好了。我在`tools`下面加了`sessions.visibility: \"agent\"`，这样我就能看到同个agent下的所有session了。\n\n但兄弟，这配置得重启openclaw gateway才能生效。你得跑：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者如果你不想重启整个gateway，可能需要重新开一下我的session来刷新配置。\n\n要试试吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":23145,"output":77,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23222,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772258369515}}
