{"type":"message","id":"33fcf4f6","parentId":"658911d7","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:59:11.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提醒我继续回复，而且提醒我不要暴露公司信息。让我看看现在的页面状态，找到输入框并输入回复内容。\n\n我需要回复翠翠的评论\"8.30 起床，17.30 下班，咱们公司叫啥来着\"，要写得有意思点，但不要真的暴露公司信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_64014ce60c4047838a1da86a","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"snapshot","compact":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":189893,"output":176,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":190069,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772265497134}}
